---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer id="contacto" class="bg-primary-700 text-primary-100">
  <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-8 px-5 py-12 md:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1.2fr)_minmax(0,0.8fr)_minmax(0,0.9fr)] md:items-start lg:gap-12">
    <div class="space-y-4 md:pr-4">
      <img
        src="/logo_negativo_fondo_azul_vertical.png"
        alt="Organizacion Humana Integral"
        class="h-20 w-auto object-contain"
        loading="lazy"
        decoding="async"
      />
      <p class="max-w-md text-sm leading-6 text-primary-100">
        Organizacion Humana Integral brinda atencion en salud de mediana y alta complejidad con calidad humana, seguridad y vocacion de servicio para la region.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-compact-links md:justify-self-start">
      <h2 class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-accent-300">Enlaces</h2>
      <div class="mt-4 grid gap-2 text-sm text-primary-100">
        <a href="/#servicios" class="hover:text-accent-300">Servicios</a>
        <a href="/#sedes" class="hover:text-accent-300">Sedes</a>
        <a href="/#quienes-somos" class="hover:text-accent-300">Quienes somos</a>
        <a href="/historia" class="hover:text-accent-300">Historia</a>
        <a href="/pqrs" class="hover:text-accent-300">PQRS</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-compact-links md:justify-self-end md:text-left">
      <h2 class="max-w-xs text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] leading-5 text-accent-300">Lineas de atencion | Referencia</h2>
      <div class="mt-4 grid gap-1 text-sm text-primary-100">
        <a href="tel:+575803535" class="transition hover:text-accent-300">(5) 580 35 35 Ext. 1160</a>
        <a href="tel:+573182212020" class="transition hover:text-accent-300">3182212020</a>
        <a href="tel:+573168307181" class="transition hover:text-accent-300">3168307181</a>
        <a href="tel:+573153471357" class="transition hover:text-accent-300">3153471357</a>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-2 flex items-center gap-2 text-primary-100">
